{"word":"δεξιτερός","slug":"δεξιτερός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δεξιτερός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> form of <a href='S:δεξιός'><el>δεξιός</el></a>\n<p/><i>right, the right</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>: <el>δεξιτερή</el>, like <el>δεξιά</el> (<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>χείρ</el>), <i>the right hand</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; epic <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> <el>δεξιτερῆιφι</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}